summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to the Yesler-Atlantic Neighborhood Improvement Project (No. Wash. R-5); authorizing acquisition of property in blocks 13 and 19 of H. L. Yesler's 1st Addition to the City of Seattle; H. L. Yesler's Donation Claim No. 47; Blocks 2, 6, 21, 23, 24 and 33 of Hill Tract Addition to the City of Seattle; Block 17 of Hill Tract Addition to the City of Seattle, Supplemental Plat; Blocks 1, 2, 3, 7, 11 and 14 of Jackson St. Addition to the City of Seattle; Blocks 1 and 2 of Burke's Second Addition to the City of Seattle; Block 6 of Rainier Addition to the City of Seattle; and Blocks 4 and 7 of New Wilfred Addition to the City of Seattle.
